{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "siegsi-auth-collection",
		"name": "SIEGSI - Autenticación",
		"description": "Colección de Postman para probar los endpoints de autenticación del sistema SIEGSI.\n\n## Instrucciones de uso:\n1. Ejecuta el endpoint de **Login** primero\n2. El token se guardará automáticamente en la variable `jwt_token`\n3. Los demás endpoints usarán ese token automáticamente\n4. Para renovar el token, usa el endpoint **Refresh Token**",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "1. Login",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"// Guardar el token automáticamente",
							"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
							"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    pm.environment.set(\"jwt_token\", jsonData.token);",
							"    pm.environment.set(\"username\", jsonData.username);",
							"    pm.environment.set(\"rolename\", jsonData.rolename);",
							"    console.log(\"✅ Token guardado exitosamente\");",
							"    console.log(\"Usuario: \" + jsonData.username);",
							"    console.log(\"Rol: \" + jsonData.rolename);",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/login",
					"host": [
						"{{base_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"login"
					]
				},
				"description": "Autentica un usuario y devuelve un token JWT válido por 24 horas.\n\nEl token se guarda automáticamente en la variable `jwt_token` para ser usado en las siguientes peticiones.\n\n**Ejemplo de respuesta exitosa:**\n```json\n{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"rolename\": \"ADMIN\",\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\"\n}\n```"
			},
			"response": [
				{
					"name": "Login Exitoso",
					"originalRequest": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "http://localhost:9090/login",
							"protocol": "http",
							"host": [
								"localhost"
							],
							"port": "9090",
							"path": [
								"login"
							]
						}
					},
					"status": "OK",
					"code": 200,
					"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
					"header": [
						{
							"key": "Content-Type",
							"value": "application/json"
						}
					],
					"body": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"rolename\": \"ADMIN\",\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhZG1pbiIsImlhdCI6MTYwOTQ1OTIwMCwiZXhwIjoxNjA5NTQ1NjAwfQ.abc123...\"\n}"
				},
				{
					"name": "Credenciales Inválidas",
					"originalRequest": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"wrong_password\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "http://localhost:9090/login",
							"protocol": "http",
							"host": [
								"localhost"
							],
							"port": "9090",
							"path": [
								"login"
							]
						}
					},
					"status": "Unauthorized",
					"code": 401,
					"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
					"header": [
						{
							"key": "Content-Type",
							"value": "application/json"
						}
					],
					"body": "{\n  \"error\": \"Credenciales inválidas\",\n  \"mensaje\": \"Clave incorrecta\"\n}"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "2. Refresh Token",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"// Actualizar el token automáticamente",
							"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
							"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    pm.environment.set(\"jwt_token\", jsonData.token);",
							"    console.log(\"✅ Token renovado exitosamente\");",
							"    console.log(\"Usuario: \" + jsonData.username);",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				},
				{
					"listen": "prerequest",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"// Verificar que existe un token",
							"var token = pm.environment.get(\"jwt_token\");",
							"if (!token) {",
							"    console.log(\"⚠️ No hay token guardado. Ejecuta primero el endpoint de Login.\");",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{jwt_token}}\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/login/refresh",
					"host": [
						"{{base_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"login",
						"refresh"
					]
				},
				"description": "Renueva un token JWT existente sin necesidad de volver a autenticarse.\n\nEl token actual debe estar válido (no expirado) para poder ser renovado.\n\nEl nuevo token se guarda automáticamente reemplazando el anterior.\n\n**Ejemplo de respuesta exitosa:**\n```json\n{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n  \"message\": \"Token renovado exitosamente\"\n}\n```"
			},
			"response": [
				{
					"name": "Token Renovado",
					"originalRequest": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhZG1pbiIsImlhdCI6MTYwOTQ1OTIwMCwiZXhwIjoxNjA5NTQ1NjAwfQ.abc123...\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "http://localhost:9090/login/refresh",
							"protocol": "http",
							"host": [
								"localhost"
							],
							"port": "9090",
							"path": [
								"login",
								"refresh"
							]
						}
					},
					"status": "OK",
					"code": 200,
					"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
					"header": [
						{
							"key": "Content-Type",
							"value": "application/json"
						}
					],
					"body": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJhZG1pbiIsImlhdCI6MTYwOTQ1OTMwMCwiZXhwIjoxNjA5NTQ1NzAwfQ.xyz789...\",\n  \"message\": \"Token renovado exitosamente\"\n}"
				},
				{
					"name": "Token Inválido",
					"originalRequest": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"token_invalido\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "http://localhost:9090/login/refresh",
							"protocol": "http",
							"host": [
								"localhost"
							],
							"port": "9090",
							"path": [
								"login",
								"refresh"
							]
						}
					},
					"status": "Unauthorized",
					"code": 401,
					"_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
					"header": [
						{
							"key": "Content-Type",
							"value": "application/json"
						}
					],
					"body": "{\n  \"error\": \"Token inválido o expirado\",\n  \"mensaje\": \"JWT strings must contain exactly 2 period characters\"\n}"
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "3. Cambiar Nombre de Usuario",
			"request": {
				"auth": {
					"type": "bearer",
					"bearer": [
						{
							"key": "token",
							"value": "{{jwt_token}}",
							"type": "string"
						}
					]
				},
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"usernameOld\": \"admin\",\n  \"usernameNew\": \"adminNew\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/login/changeUsername",
					"host": [
						"{{base_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"login",
						"changeUsername"
					]
				},
				"description": "Cambia el nombre de usuario. Requiere autenticación JWT.\n\nEl nuevo nombre debe ser diferente al actual y se requiere la contraseña para confirmar."
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "4. Cambiar Contraseña",
			"request": {
				"auth": {
					"type": "bearer",
					"bearer": [
						{
							"key": "token",
							"value": "{{jwt_token}}",
							"type": "string"
						}
					]
				},
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"passwordOld\": \"password123\",\n  \"passwordNew\": \"newPassword456\"\n}"
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/login/changePassword",
					"host": [
						"{{base_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"login",
						"changePassword"
					]
				},
				"description": "Cambia la contraseña del usuario. Requiere autenticación JWT.\n\nLa nueva contraseña debe ser diferente a la actual."
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "5. Health Check",
			"request": {
				"method": "GET",
				"header": [],
